seo: weblogic,任意文件上传,CVE-2018-2894,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测WebLogic服务器是否存在ws_utc任意文件上传漏洞（CVE-2018-2894），通过发送特定请求判断漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the WebLogic server has the ws_utc arbitrary file upload vulnerability (CVE-2018-2894) by sending specific requests to determine if the vulnerability exists.
